{"tid":2413930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫療事故死因研訊　陪審員中途突稱不諳廣東話　裁判官下令解散陪審團擇日重審","createTime":"2021-02-19T05:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T05:35:32.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c237bb4644287efcb492a8a4628c5bed710b6cd","tid":2413930,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3wQSpjFUET3UXZA_IrYMZMqpCts=/5252x2954/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WWNMLL2C5VFI7FLT2I7WEVFW34.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3wQSpjFUET3UXZA_IrYMZMqpCts%3D%2F5252x2954%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWWNMLL2C5VFI7FLT2I7WEVFW34.JPG&h=dc563ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者的兒子（右）及媳婦今日到庭參與死因研訊。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n瑪麗醫院2016年5月發生醫療事故，有護士為一名坐在扶手椅上的病人拔除血液透析導管時，疑沒跟隨「頭低腳高」指引，導致病人空氣栓塞，需即時急救，延醫3日後不治。涉事護士被控2項專業失當罪，最終被護士管理局裁定罪成，判處除牌5個月。死因庭原定今就事件召開研訊，並已選出4男1女組成的陪審團。惟研訊進行約一小時後，一名男陪審員突然表示其母語為國語，不諳廣東話，聽不懂證供中的某些詞彙。死因裁判官黃偉權遂下令解散陪審團，擇日再審。<br />\n<br />\n事緣證人今早作供逾一小時後，有男陪審員在提問時段表示不明白證供中的某些詞彙。在死因裁判官進一步追問下，該陪審員表示平時交談多數用國語及英語，至於廣東話則僅「聽得明七、八成」。死因裁判官指為免構成不公平情況，決定解散陪審團，並將重新篩選陪審員，排期重審。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/VZC6BJKVOFH2ZJRJZT6KCYUGCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FVZC6BJKVOFH2ZJRJZT6KCYUGCI%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=8e19e786\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FVZC6BJKVOFH2ZJRJZT6KCYUGCI%2F&h=06b7aa9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/VZC6BJKVOFH2ZJRJZT6KCYUGCI/</a>"},{"pid":"eb4c5edf06630b76455eb8ff0c58f81c58149ee7","tid":2413930,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:23:06.000Z","msg":"玩野呀屌"},{"pid":"74d472806f1783e898287b1105d233222915f3cd","tid":2413930,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:35:32.000Z","msg":"必須搞清楚國語係指台語定支語，文中無講，但絕不可以將支語當成國語"}]}